These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
2 different games are played: canasta, snooker
City: london, berlin
1. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
3. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Pet      | fish     | chinchilla      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Game         | snooker   | canasta |
| City   | london  | berlin      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, musical
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, red
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, punk
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the fan of disco is not the person who likes red##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Movie-Genre    | mystery        | musical    |
| Color       | purple         | red |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Music-Genre   | disco               | punk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, bike
City: liverpool, new-york
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | daisy |
| Transport   | boat       | bike    |
| City   | liverpool | new-york |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
