1. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
2. the tower house is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| House         | futuristic | tower  |
| Color           | apricot  | black |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola   |
| Transport     | tram   | airplane |

