There are 2 different nationalities: polish, chinese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, tennis
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the fan of country is not to the left of the chinese##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the fan of pop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Music-Genre        | country | pop            |
| Nationality       | chinese | polish              |
| Sport         | badminton  | tennis |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

