The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, surfing
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, dancing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower
1. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Food          | plum         | corn    |
| Sport           | basketball | surfing   |
| Hobby   | singing   | dancing    |
| Flower     | sunflower         | bellflower |

 